State.Author: Ceo
State.Description: OSex brings award winning and tasteful intimacy, romance and sex to Skyrim. It features thousands of scenes all seamlessly connected with movement where you control every action through beautifully illustrated interactive menus. Each animation is hand crafted with charm and detail by one of Skyrim's most legendary animators, Ceo.
